Class OvernightIndexCurveMapping

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.opengamma.strata.function.marketdata.mapping.OvernightIndexCurveMapping
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MarketDataMapping<Curve,OvernightIndexCurveKey>, Serializable, Bean, ImmutableBean

    public final class OvernightIndexCurveMapping
extends Object
implements MarketDataMapping<Curve,OvernightIndexCurveKey>, ImmutableBean, Serializable
    Market data mapping that accepts a OvernightIndexCurveKey and returns a OvernightIndexCurveId with the name of the curve group that is the source of the curve.

      • getIdForKey

        public OvernightIndexCurveId getIdForKey(OvernightIndexCurveKey key)
        Description copied from interface: MarketDataMapping
        Returns a market data ID which uniquely identifies the piece of market data referred to by the key.

        The key might identify an item of data of which there are many instances in the system, for example the USD discounting curve. The ID identifies a globally unique instance, for example the USD discounting curve from a named curve group.

        Specified by:
        getIdForKey in interface MarketDataMapping<Curve,OvernightIndexCurveKey>
        Parameters:
        key - a key identifying an item of market data
        Returns:
        an ID uniquely identifying an item of market data
